      <div class="msgContentFrame">This doesn't apply directly to konschtat, but I did this quest in other zones by doing these steps: <br />- Get A mightier martello <br />- Upgrade a martello just before the day changes (in instances I did this, the martello dropped to 88%) <br />- Get Refuel and replenish <br />- Refuel the upgraded martello <br /> <br />Now, if you know someone who does have a high enough rank in Konschtat, you can just ask him to upgrade the martello with you there and then refuel it yourself right away. Good luck finding someone with that much fame tho.<div class="msgSig"><div class="msgSigBar sm">----------------------------</div><pre>Rank: Bastok 10, San d'Oria 10, Windurst 10 
