      <div class="msgContentFrame">Actually, in Konschtat you are forced onto a certain path of quests that you MUST complete before you can move past fame level 1 and onto any further quests.  Refuel and Replenish is one of those quests.  It's the only zone where you have to complete it before you can possibly do A Mightier Martello, among other things.</div>
